These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-1::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  coach, chef, photographer, firefighter, architect
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, animation, horror, scientific, martial-arts
 1. the architect is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
 2. the coach is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the person watching animation movies is the coach##1
 4. the firefighter is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 6. the architect is not to the right of the person watching scientific movies##8
 7. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
 8. the architect is not the person watching horror movies##6
 9. the photographer is on the left or right of the chef##3
10. the person watching family movies is not the firefighter##6
11. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
12. the firefighter is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
13. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the person watching horror movies##8
14. the photographer is somewhere between the architect and the person watching horror movies##7
15. the coach is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5     |
| Job        | chef | photographer | architect | firefighter     | coach    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | martial-arts       | family   | scientific | animation |

