.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-2::.
5 different pets are kept: dog, guinea-pig, chinchilla, turtle, frog
There are 5 different favourite colors: turquise, red, green, white, yellow
 1. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 2. the person who likes yellow is not to the left of the person who likes turquise##8
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person who likes green##5
 4. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
 5. the owner of the frog is not to the right of the owner of the dog##8
 6. the person who likes red is not the owner of the dog##6
 7. the person who likes turquise is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
10. the owner of the frog is not to the right of the owner of the dog##8
11. the owner of the dog is the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| Pet   | turtle | frog    | dog | guinea-pig  | chinchilla |
| Color   | turquise  | white | yellow      | red | green |

