.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-3::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, daffodil, daisy, bellflower, amaryllis
5 different pets are kept: frog, cat, lizard, hedgehog, pony
1. the person who growsorchid is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
2. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
3. the person who growsdaffodil is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person who growsbellflower##2
4. the person who growsdaffodil is the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is in the middle##1
6. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
7. the person who growsorchid is not to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |       3        |     4     |     5     |
| Flower           | bellflower | daffodil | amaryllis | orchid | daisy  |
| Pet   | cat  | lizard        | hedgehog          | pony     | frog |

