.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-4::.
House: gothic-revival, victorian, art-deco, ranch-style, modern
There are 5 different favourite colors: lavender, blood-red, coral, orange, ivory
 1. the gothic-revival house is somewhere between the victorian house and the person who likes lavender##7
 2. the person who likes coral is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
 4. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ivory##5
 5. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1
 6. the person who likes blood-red is not the art-deco house##6
 7. the victorian house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 8. the modern house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
 9. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere between the art-deco house and the gothic-revival house##7
10. the person who likes blood-red is not to the right of the victorian house##8
11. the ranch-style house is the ranch-style house##1
12. the person who likes blood-red is not the ranch-style house##6
13. the person who likes orange is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
14. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |
| House   | art-deco | modern | ranch-style | gothic-revival | victorian |
| Color           | lavender    | blood-red | ivory    | orange      | coral      |

