.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-5::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, dunhill, tiparillo, bluemaster, ritmeester
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, february, march, august, may
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
 2. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 3. the ritmeester-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in august##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is the vegafina-smoker##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is not to the left of the vegafina-smoker##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 8. the tiparillo-smoker is between the vegafina-smoker and the ritmeester-smoker##2
 9. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
10. the dunhill-smoker is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |    3    |   4   |    5    |
| Cigar      | dunhill   | vegafina  | tiparillo    | ritmeester | bluemaster |
| Birthday   | december | may | august | february | march   |

