 5. the fan of pop is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 7. the fan of trance is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the fan of rock is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the fan of pop is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in october##7
10. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
11. the fan of pop is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
12. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
