 3. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
 5. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 6. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 9. the person driving the subway is not the person drinking milk##6
10. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Beverage   | milk     | sprite | coffee | lemonade | hot-chocolate |
| Transport           | train | snowmobile   | subway  | boat    | roller     |

